<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 12:13:03 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>真主党向以色列北部发射了三十枚火箭弹；无人机在梅图拉爆炸</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-06/ty-article/.premium/thirty-rockets-fired-at-israels-north-by-hezbollah-drone-explodes-in-metula/0000018f-4d4c-dd3a-a5cf-7f7feeb20000</link><description>美国消息人士最近表示，加沙停火将为与真主党和黎巴嫩谈判达成协议以结束与以色列的敌对行动创造必要条件</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 11:05:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-06/ty-article/.premium/thirty-rockets-fired-at-israels-north-by-hezbollah-drone-explodes-in-metula/0000018f-4d4c-dd3a-a5cf-7f7feeb20000</guid></item><item><title>以色列欧洲电视网代表出席大屠杀纪念仪式而不是开幕活动</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-06/ty-article/.premium/israeli-eurovision-singer-attends-holocaust-memorial-ceremony-instead-of-opening-event/0000018f-4d60-d17f-adcf-fde3f8020000</link><description>出于安全考虑，戈兰和她的团队此前曾表示，除了排练和她的实际表演之外，他们不会参加任何欧洲歌唱大赛的活动。周日，这位以色列歌手在马尔默犹太社区举行的小型大屠杀纪念仪式上点燃了蜡烛</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 10:50:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-06/ty-article/.premium/israeli-eurovision-singer-attends-holocaust-memorial-ceremony-instead-of-opening-event/0000018f-4d60-d17f-adcf-fde3f8020000</guid></item><item><title>加沙医疗消息人士称，以色列在地面行动之前开始撤离，拉法有 26 人死亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-05-06/ty-article/.premium/israel-begins-evacuation-of-civilians-from-rafah-defense-chief-says-hamas-left-no-choice/0000018f-4cf7-dcda-abcf-6ef708a20000</link><description>以色列国防军估计，加沙南部社区约有10万居民被勒令撤离，但军方消息人士称，这只是有限行动，并没有完全撤离拉法</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 10:15:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-05-06/ty-article/.premium/israel-begins-evacuation-of-civilians-from-rafah-defense-chief-says-hamas-left-no-choice/0000018f-4cf7-dcda-abcf-6ef708a20000</guid></item><item><title>在加沙拥挤的战场上，许多以色列士兵被友军炮火打死</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-06/ty-article/.premium/on-gazas-crowded-battlefields-many-israeli-soldiers-are-killed-by-friendly-fire/0000018f-4cee-d414-a5bf-ffff3da30000</link><description>上周，两名预备役军人在加沙被以色列坦克炮火误认为敌人而身亡。一名中队指挥官就该事件表示：“以我们现有的手段，这种情况可能会再次发生”</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 09:24:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-06/ty-article/.premium/on-gazas-crowded-battlefields-many-israeli-soldiers-are-killed-by-friendly-fire/0000018f-4cee-d414-a5bf-ffff3da30000</guid></item><item><title>十年前的以色列法律可能会阻碍与黎巴嫩真主党的冲突缓和</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-06/ty-article/.premium/a-decade-old-israeli-law-could-hamper-deescalation-with-hezbollah-in-lebanon/0000018f-4cb7-d414-a5bf-ffb73eb60000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡政府2014年通过的一项法律规定，任何以色列领土的割让都必须经过全民公投或议会多数席位的批准，这可能会影响总理确保以色列北部与黎巴嫩边境保持平静的能力</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 09:01:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-06/ty-article/.premium/a-decade-old-israeli-law-could-hamper-deescalation-with-hezbollah-in-lebanon/0000018f-4cb7-d414-a5bf-ffb73eb60000</guid></item><item><title>以色列通过敬献花圈和大屠杀纪念馆纪念大屠杀纪念日</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-06/ty-article/.premium/israel-marks-holocaust-remembrance-day-with-wreath-laying-yad-vashem-ceremony/0000018f-4c7d-d414-a5bf-ff7fa1560000</link><description>随着警报声使国家陷入停顿，全国各地将举行仪式。周日晚上，内塔尼亚胡在大屠杀纪念馆举行的一次活动中表示，“即使我们必须孤立无援，我们也将继续与人类的邪恶作斗争”</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 06:24:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-06/ty-article/.premium/israel-marks-holocaust-remembrance-day-with-wreath-laying-yad-vashem-ceremony/0000018f-4c7d-d414-a5bf-ff7fa1560000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯谈判濒临崩溃，内塔尼亚胡摆出了拒绝主义的姿态</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-06/ty-article/.premium/with-hamas-talks-on-the-verge-of-collapse-netanyahu-puts-up-a-rejectionist-front/0000018f-4a51-d6c3-afdf-4f530dfb0000</link><description>中央情报局局长被派往中东，努力挽救人质协议，而内塔尼亚胡被认为是主要障碍。美国压力的大小将决定他是否答应拜登总统的要求</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 03:02:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-06/ty-article/.premium/with-hamas-talks-on-the-verge-of-collapse-netanyahu-puts-up-a-rejectionist-front/0000018f-4a51-d6c3-afdf-4f530dfb0000</guid></item><item><title>关闭半岛电视台是以色列搬起石头砸自己的脚</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-05-06/ty-article/.premium/by-shutting-down-al-jazeera-israel-is-shooting-itself-in-the-foot/0000018f-4a76-dcda-abcf-6a77785b0000</link><description>通过关闭卡塔尔新闻网络，以色列加入了一个由阿拉伯国家组成的杰出俱乐部，该俱乐部已经停止了半岛电视台的运营。此举应该令以色列媒体感到担忧，因为以色列媒体被禁止在加沙地带内部独立进行广播</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 03:01:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-05-06/ty-article/.premium/by-shutting-down-al-jazeera-israel-is-shooting-itself-in-the-foot/0000018f-4a76-dcda-abcf-6a77785b0000</guid></item><item><title>无人机在以色列北部爆炸；以色列国防军公布了在加沙边境火箭弹袭击中丧生的第四名士兵的名字</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-06/ty-article-live/idf-three-soldiers-killed-near-gaza-border/0000018f-4ba4-dcda-abcf-6ba7979b0006</link><description>爆炸性无人机袭击以色列北部城镇，以色列国防军进行报复 ■ 以色列国防部长：哈马斯别无选择，只能开始拉法攻势 ■ 以色列国防军开始从拉法东郊疏散约 10 万巴勒斯坦人 ■ 哈马斯对加沙边境的火箭袭击造成 4 名士兵死亡，9 人受伤■ 哈马斯重申人质交易的起点是结束战争</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 02:30:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-06/ty-article-live/idf-three-soldiers-killed-near-gaza-border/0000018f-4ba4-dcda-abcf-6ba7979b0006</guid></item><item><title>以色列中部和北部夜间发生枪击事件，两名男子丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-06/ty-article/.premium/two-men-killed-in-overnight-shootings-in-central-and-northern-israel/0000018f-4bfe-dcda-abcf-6bff97570000</link><description>警方怀疑至少其中一起事件与有组织犯罪有关</description><pubDate>Sun, 05 May 2024 21:51:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-06/ty-article/.premium/two-men-killed-in-overnight-shootings-in-central-and-northern-israel/0000018f-4bfe-dcda-abcf-6bff97570000</guid></item><item><title>以色列政府抛弃了其公民。但反对派几乎没有希望</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-05-05/ty-article/.highlight/israels-government-has-abandoned-its-citizens-but-the-opposition-offers-little-hope/0000018f-49cc-d6c3-afdf-4ddf0a700000</link><description>每一位宁愿与本格维尔和内塔尼亚胡共处一室，也不愿在街头与那些呼喊他们的人在一起的以色列民选官员都选择了错误的一边</description><pubDate>Sun, 05 May 2024 20:58:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-05-05/ty-article/.highlight/israels-government-has-abandoned-its-citizens-but-the-opposition-offers-little-hope/0000018f-49cc-d6c3-afdf-4ddf0a700000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军公布了在加沙火箭弹袭击中丧生的四名士兵的名字</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-05/ty-article/.premium/idf-names-three-soldiers-killed-in-mortar-barrage-from-gaza/0000018f-4a7b-d91a-a5af-ebffec900000</link><description>塔尔·沙维特、鲁本·马克·莫迪凯·阿苏林、伊多·泰斯塔和迈克尔·鲁扎尔这四名士兵正在看守军队在拉法行动之前部署的装备。哈马斯袭击中另有九名士兵受伤</description><pubDate>Sun, 05 May 2024 20:56:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-05/ty-article/.premium/idf-names-three-soldiers-killed-in-mortar-barrage-from-gaza/0000018f-4a7b-d91a-a5af-ebffec900000</guid></item><item><title>据报道加沙停火谈判陷入“困境”，中央情报局局长前往以色列挽救协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-05/ty-article/.premium/gaza-cease-fire-talks-reportedly-in-tough-spot-cia-chief-heads-to-israel-to-rescue-deal/0000018f-4a4b-d17f-adcf-fbebfac90000</link><description>参与谈判的消息人士称，尽管哈马斯做出了积极回应，但以色列拒绝派遣代表团前往埃及讨论该协议。哈马斯重申立场 要求以色列全面撤出加沙</description><pubDate>Sun, 05 May 2024 20:23:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-05/ty-article/.premium/gaza-cease-fire-talks-reportedly-in-tough-spot-cia-chief-heads-to-israel-to-rescue-deal/0000018f-4a4b-d17f-adcf-fbebfac90000</guid></item><item><title>尽管气氛充满敌意，以色列的铁杆粉丝仍希望在马尔默为欧洲歌唱大赛加油</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-05/ty-article/.premium/die-hard-israeli-fans-hope-to-cheer-on-eurovision-in-malmo-despite-hostile-vibes/0000018f-48e4-d414-a5bf-fbf7bcfe0000</link><description>决定前往瑞典马尔默的球迷表示，他们并不担心计划中的反以色列示威活动，但在赛场外“不想引起注意”或让其他人知道他们是以色列人</description><pubDate>Sun, 05 May 2024 18:41:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-05/ty-article/.premium/die-hard-israeli-fans-hope-to-cheer-on-eurovision-in-malmo-despite-hostile-vibes/0000018f-48e4-d414-a5bf-fbf7bcfe0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列选择在10月7日点燃独立日火炬 行动因威胁而取消</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-05/ty-article/.premium/israeli-chosen-to-light-independence-day-torch-cancels-due-to-threats/0000018f-491d-d17f-adcf-f9ffcc3f0000</link><description>以色列南部莫沙夫亚泰德的居民纳斯林·优素福 (Nasreen Yousef) 审问了 10 月 7 日渗透到她所在地区的恐怖分子，但社区反应小组的成员表示，她夸大了自己在挫败袭击中的作用。她说她取消是因为她和她的家人受到威胁</description><pubDate>Sun, 05 May 2024 18:19:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-05/ty-article/.premium/israeli-chosen-to-light-independence-day-torch-cancels-due-to-threats/0000018f-491d-d17f-adcf-f9ffcc3f0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第 212 天：中央情报局局长前往多哈与卡塔尔总理举行紧急会议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-05-05/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-212-cia-chief-travels-to-doha-for-emergency-meeting-with-qatari-pm/0000018f-49ab-d414-a5bf-fbbfede50001</link><description>总理内塔尼亚胡表示“以色列不能接受”哈马斯结束加沙战争的要求 ■ 以色列国防部长：哈马斯显示出不打算达成协议的迹象，这意味着拉法行动将在“不久的将来”启动 ■ 中央情报局局长伯恩斯出差前往多哈与卡塔尔总理举行紧急会议 ■ 内塔尼亚胡政府一致投票决定关闭以色列半岛电视台 ■ 战争进入 212 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Sun, 05 May 2024 16:59:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-05-05/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-212-cia-chief-travels-to-doha-for-emergency-meeting-with-qatari-pm/0000018f-49ab-d414-a5bf-fbbfede50001</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡和辛瓦尔都需要获胜，因此加沙战争将继续下去</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-05/ty-article/.premium/both-netanyahu-and-sinwar-need-to-win-so-the-gaza-war-will-carry-on/0000018f-4978-d6c3-afdf-4d7bac470000</link><description>大多数以色列人和加沙人都明白，他们失去了太多，在这场战争中没有任何“胜利”的概念。但只要他们的命运掌握在两个坚持成为胜利者的人手中，不惜一切代价，这场战争就会继续下去</description><pubDate>Sun, 05 May 2024 16:37:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-05/ty-article/.premium/both-netanyahu-and-sinwar-need-to-win-so-the-gaza-war-will-carry-on/0000018f-4978-d6c3-afdf-4d7bac470000</guid></item><item><title>真主党向以色列北部发射重型火箭弹；大楼被撞，两人受伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-05/ty-article/.premium/hezbollah-fires-heavy-rocket-barrages-at-northern-israel-building-hit-two-wounded/0000018f-496b-d6c3-afdf-4d7bba610000</link><description>以色列军方称，从黎巴嫩向上加利利发射了约 40 枚火箭弹。作为回应，以色列袭击了黎巴嫩真主党目标；黎巴嫩新闻媒体报道四名平民死亡、两人受伤</description><pubDate>Sun, 05 May 2024 16:18:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-05/ty-article/.premium/hezbollah-fires-heavy-rocket-barrages-at-northern-israel-building-hit-two-wounded/0000018f-496b-d6c3-afdf-4d7bba610000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡表示，以色列不能接受哈马斯结束加沙战争的要求；国防部长：拉法攻势迫在眉睫</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-05/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-israel-cannot-accept-hamas-demand-to-end-war-gallant-rafah-offensive-imminent/0000018f-491b-d91a-a5af-e9ffa33f0000</link><description>据报道加沙谈判取得进展，国防部长加兰特在加沙内部表示，以色列认识到“哈马斯不打算遵守任何协议的令人震惊的迹象”；哈马斯领导人哈尼亚重申该组织的出发点是停止战争</description><pubDate>Sun, 05 May 2024 15:30:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-05/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-israel-cannot-accept-hamas-demand-to-end-war-gallant-rafah-offensive-imminent/0000018f-491b-d91a-a5af-e9ffa33f0000</guid></item><item><title>《周六夜现场》回避学生抗议，选择与家长轻松取笑</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-05-05/ty-article/.premium/snl-sidesteps-student-protests-and-opts-for-lighthearted-fun-at-their-parents/0000018f-48e1-d17f-adcf-f9e318340000</link><description>该短剧以脱口秀圆桌会议为特色，主持人询问家长对抗议活动的感受</description><pubDate>Sun, 05 May 2024 15:04:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-05-05/ty-article/.premium/snl-sidesteps-student-protests-and-opts-for-lighthearted-fun-at-their-parents/0000018f-48e1-d17f-adcf-f9e318340000</guid></item></channel></rss>